      <LongDescription>The &lt;noparse&gt;SGM-H-300 Pain Train&lt;/noparse&gt; is a size 3 waypoint-capable cruise missile.  It is based on the SGM-H-3 body, which is a high speed hybrid missile designed to strike heavy targets.  This missile will deliver a $MISSILEWARHEAD_DETAIL_HEKP warhead.  It homes in on its target using an Active Radar seeker, validating that it is the correct target using command guidance from its launching ship.

